<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Terms of Service - FMPG</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/logo.png" type="image/icon type">
    
    <!-- Central Tailwind CSS & Theme Config -->
    <%- include('tailwind-head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-bg-body text-text-primary min-h-screen flex flex-col transition-colors duration-300">
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('header') %>

    <!-- Header Banner -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/5 to-transparent border-b border-border-color/60">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center space-y-2">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold font-heading text-primary">Terms of Service</h1>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm md:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">Please review the official guidelines, tenant preferences, security measures, and verification protocols for listing a property on FMPG.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Workspace -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start animate-fade-in-up">
            
            <!-- Quick Sidebar Index Navigation -->
            <aside class="md:col-span-4 sticky top-24 bg-bg-card/40 border border-border-color/60 rounded-2xl p-5 space-y-3 hidden md:block">
                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-border-color pb-2 mb-3">Service Index</h4>
                <nav class="space-y-2 text-xs font-semibold text-text-secondary">
                    <a href="#accuracy" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">1. Accuracy & Verification</a>
                    <a href="#listing-duration" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">2. Duration of Listings</a>
                    <a href="#fees" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">3. Fees & Commission</a>
                    <a href="#security" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">4. Security Measures</a>
                    <a href="#payments" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">5. Payment Methods</a>
                    <a href="#verification" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">6. Tenant Verification</a>
                    <a href="#privacy" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">7. Data Privacy</a>
                </nav>
            </aside>

            <!-- Detailed Policy Blocks -->
            <article class="md:col-span-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 border border-border-color shadow-xl space-y-8 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                
                <!-- Section 1 -->
                <section id="accuracy" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        1. Accuracy of Information & Listings
                    </h2>
                    <p>By listing your PG on our platform, you agree to provide complete, accurate, and up-to-date information about the accommodation rooms, capacity, and amenities.</p>
                    <p>FMPG reserves the right to audit, verify, or temporarily modify listings to maintain data authenticity and quality standards.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 2 -->
                <section id="listing-duration" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        2. Duration of Listings
                    </h2>
                    <p>Listings remain active for 7 days, after which they can be renewed or updated by the owner. FMPG reserves the right to suspend or remove inactive, inaccurate, or non-compliant listings.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 3 -->
                <section id="fees" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        3. Fees & Commission
                    </h2>
                    <p>FMPG may charge a standard commission or service fee from successful PG bookings as per prior mutual agreements signed during owner onboarding.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 4 -->
                <section id="security" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        4. Security & Safety Measures
                    </h2>
                    <p>Listed accommodations are highly advised to provide proper security measures such as CCTV cameras, secure gated entry, and lockable individual storage lockers for tenant personal belongings.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 5 -->
                <section id="payments" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        5. Payment Timelines
                    </h2>
                    <p>Clarity on monthly rent timelines (e.g. rent due dates, security deposit refund terms, and late-payment penalties) must be transparently declared in your EJS listing form.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 6 -->
                <section id="verification" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        6. Verification of Tenants
                    </h2>
                    <p>Owners are ultimately responsible for conducting proper tenant verification, ensuring that the guest provides valid government-issued ID and complies with local municipal bylaws.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 7 -->
                <section id="privacy" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        7. Data Privacy
                    </h2>
                    <p>All personal coordinates provided by the owner and tenants are fully protected under FMPG's secure Privacy Policy. FMPG will not sell or distribute user metrics for external marketing purposes.</p>
                </section>

            </article>

        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('footer') %>
</body>

</html>